<TEXT type="str">Seven billion people on earth. One terrifying virus that could destroy them all. When a lethal virus developed at a top secret laboratory falls into the hands of international terrorists, humanity teeters on the brink of a global apocalypse. A few drops released into the atmosphere could trigger a worldwide pandemic – unless Tom Blake can thwart their deadly plans.Summoned to investigate a mysterious assassination, the former Special Forces psychologist with a haunted past is dispatched undercover into a high-security jail where he uncovers the plot to steal the virus.Teamed up with Alex Mortensen, one of the security service’s rising stars, Blake heads for northern Europe on a perilous adventure, hot on the heels of the thieves in a desperate race against time that will pitch them against one of the world’s most dangerous men.Their mission takes them to the wilds of Scotland, and across the freezing North Sea to Norway – and beyond into the dark heart of Soviet Russia.The Armageddon Virus is a breath-taking, lightning-paced thriller – the second in the Tom Blake Thriller series‘Fast, furious and more twists than a coiled cobra.’</TEXT> 
